"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Much ado about nothing is the appropriate description for many projects in the “metaverse” with no live product.\\n\\n$SAND $UFO some projects breaking in the top 100 have backing from big names, but no live product. The gamble seems to be that gamers will migrate to crypto for the opportunity of sweet, sweet gains.  \\n  \\n The response so far had been cringe-worthy. Many prominent streaming gamers with communities of viewers are rejecting crypto gaming as deceptive. \\n \\n\\nI dont think crypto games will see the same adoption as corporate released games without some extreme marketing. The biggest consumers of these products are children aged 5-15. These online gaming economies will remain in a silo without any bridge to IRL. \\n\\nKids will grow out of these titles and into lives in the actual-verse. so what is the bet? that some kid 20 years from now will want to pay me for my hoverboard NFT because its vintage?\\n\\nThere is a bull run, so there is there is money to be made, but it looks like crypto gaming is already turning in to a bubble. I give it 4-6 years of life.\\n\\nThere is probably more to write about this. and one day, I will but for now i published something on a decentralized publishing platform and thats pretty sweet.\",\"timestamp\":1637884079,\"title\":\"Gaming Tokens sans Product\"},\"digest\":\"y13oiE6f53C35JR6O4WTtFU0SpHTD9xZ7rKdUbgTm_Q\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x68Fe59cAB5f2D38751b72D8F08de70bFF8244690\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"GuvhngMGGWKuo1y-dbDf46AU9csVD4PVoSOoGy5EqaM\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"EbBap5DKDBXw8gbmxcuJJfor_qIWRR5ouDTai06W9gw\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"yZY81B4rAUFLPmCEIdT9J_VnkDn_7VG93L2Joi5PKlt0ZaB1x2hekFMtia5IAWQrVHOjdZaAhyOEo70zsEJMCA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xc56f17e3fea3d2b1e9bd6aeaa68fd21271fa93e5797ee83787e06ea60a4f03095e2141a82da424e432ca72a9c49bc3ca374b0965fa06edcacc7f423895544b501c\